  <brief_title>Can Structured Education Promote Physical Activity in Those Identified With an Increased Risk of Developing Diabetes</brief_title>
  <acronym>PREPARE</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomised Controlled Trial to Investigate the Effect of a Structured Educational Programme on Physical Activity Levels and Glucose Tolerance in People With Impaired Glucose Tolerance</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
